Solutions for International Investors

 






 

 
FIL Limited, Fidelity Investments Canada Limited, Fidelity Investments Management (H.K.) Limited, Fidelity Investments Japan, and Fidelity Brokerage Services Japan LLC offer products and services designed specifically for overseas investors. These non-U.S. entities do not offer these products or services outside their intended countries or regions, and purchase orders from U.S. investors will not be accepted. To reach the web site of these non-U.S. entities, please select from those listed below.
			The information available through accessing FIL Limited, Fidelity Investments Canada Limited, Fidelity Investments Management (H.K.) Limited, Fidelity Investments Japan, or Fidelity Brokerage Services Japan LLC has been prepared and is maintained by those non-U.S. entities. Access to this material by U.S. residents is for informational purposes only and should not be construed as an offer to sell, a solicitation of an offer to buy, or a recommendation for any security under U.S. law. All content contained therein should be considered, and is subject to, the specific regulatory requirements under which FIL Limited, Fidelity Investments Canada Limited, Fidelity Investments Management (H.K.) Limited, Fidelity Investments Japan, or Fidelity Brokerage Services Japan LLC operate, respectively. Fidelity funds are offered by prospectus only.
